name: NuminaMath 1.5
summary: Math problems with Chain of Thought (CoT) solutions.
notes: The problems are compiled from Chinese high-school math problems (30%), Olympiads (22%) Orca-Math (17%, itself a compilation), synthetic data (16%), AoPS, AMC, AIME, GSM8k, MATH... Some problems requires a correct proof, other a numerical or symbolic expression.
